channel.title: Looking to start up a team
channel.description:
I'm looking to start up a server. 317, 508, 600+ It doesn't really matter to me. Just looking for some other coders, maybe some people that'd be interested in hosting, etc. Basically a team, that together we could go through the process. I'm looking for: Coders 0/ (as many as needed) Staff Leader 0/1(Owner) Admin 0/1 Mod 0/2 Player Help 0/3
Let me know. Will be updating any progress.
